00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,600
My plea for aid was met only with silence along this path.

2
00:00:04,500 --> 00:00:07,600
But in turn, I've sinned through it all.

3
00:00:08,400 --> 00:00:10,100
My mind is made, friend.

4
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:13,000
I shall rely on none but myself.

5
00:00:13,900 --> 00:00:17,300
If none shall aid, I will act on my own.

6
00:00:17,900 --> 00:00:23,300
Should our paths cross at the Flaming Mountains, we'll toast to our reunion.

7
00:00:24,900 --> 00:00:27,700
Now, take great care.

